snippet.title: Best VGM 713 - Crusader of Centy - Root Temple
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1256 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1DwQk4-Smn0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Genesis
Crusader of Centy / Soleil (1994)
Root Temple
Motokazu Shinoda & Noriyuki Iwadare
